column1: # NCT Balloon flight aspect file for the May 17
# This file is in the following format:
#FrmC
#  01. GCU Housekeeping Frame Counter
#  02. GCU time: YY [Year] in UT
#  03. GCU time: MM [Month] in UT
#  04. GCU time: DD [Day] in UT
#  05. GCU time: hh [Hour] in UT
#  06. GCU time: mm [Minute] in UT
#  07. GCU time: ss [Second] in UT
#  08. GCU time: Linux time in second
#  09. dGPS time: Linux time in second  (hkp2.GPSTime+SECINWEEK*hkp2.GPSWeek+GPS_SEC_OFFSET) (*Note)
#  10. UHF Clock: 10 MHz clock to synchronize clocks among card cages
#  11. dGPS aspect: Latitude of the antenna beacon from dGPS
#  12. dGPS aspect: Longitude of the antenna beacon from dGPS
#  13. dGPS aspect: Altitude of the antenna beacon from dGPS
#  14. dGPS aspect: Heading of the antenna baseline from dGPS
#  15. dGPS aspect: Pitch angle of the antenna baseline from dGPS ()
#  16. dGPS aspect: Roll angle of the antenna baseline from dGPS
#  17. GPS Good flags: (from MSb to LSb) Differential-Correction
#  *Note: GPS_SEC_OFFSET=3159648001
#         number of seconds between the Unix Epoch (00:00 1 Jan 1970)
#         and the GPS Epoch (00:00 6 Jan 1980)
#         source: http://ldas-cit.ligo.caltech.edu/doc/tcl_docs/html/gpstimetcl.html
# All angles are in degrees (Heading
# This file created by Alan Chiu using gse on Feb. 26
